From: Arnaldo Carvalho de Melo <acme@redhat.com>
Date: Wed, 9 May 2012 12:21:22 -0300
Subject: [PATCH] perf hists browser: Use '/' for search/filter instead of 's'

commit 5a5626b1b4bf8467891c9297ffda979db97ed5ec upstream.

That is what is used in vi and mutt, and as well on the 'annotate'
browser.

Eventually we can have keymappings to make people used to other key
associations more confortable.

